Is this all for this time...? The members of the Mucos
organization are starting to become cautious as well.

The soldiers of the former Tomos plundering group are
saying, 'Perhaps it's time to change our location.'

Former captain of the Tomos plundering group: If it weren't
for the Adventurer's Guild, we could still be working in
Fotizona--
Former captain of the Tomos plundering group: Who's there!
Clea: I've come to defeat all of you.

Soldiers of the former Tomos plundering group: We're not
weak enough to lose to these women!

Clea: I am a member of the Adventurer's Guild, Futeira
branch. Personally, I have my own reasons to fight alongside
all of you.

Former captain of the Tomos plundering group: I've heard
something good...! I'll use it as bait to lure out Agonia
and Shimos!

Former captain of the Tomos plundering group: Capture them
alive!

Former captain of the Tomos plundering group: Whether it's
Shimos or Agonia... Are there only monsters in the
Adventurer's Guild...?
Stolge of Affection: Since we're at it, let me reminisce too.
Clea: Stolge-san, why are you in a place like this?

Stolge of Affection: I have some business with these stolen goods
of theirs for a little job.

Mage Relm: We feel the same way! Let me search first,
please!

Stolge of Affection: I-I understand. I'll guide you to the hiding
place of the stolen goods.
Mage Relm: With this, the fool's grimoire is finally...!

Stolge of Affection: The fool's grimoire, you say!?
Hehehe, ahahaha, that's a laughable joke.

Thief Nora: I-Is it really that funny? Relm-san was really
looking forward to it... *sniff*

Stolge of Affection: My apologies... I too was deceived by
the fool's grimoire.

Priestess Sophia: Are there really so many counterfeits
going around?

Stolge of Affection: A fictional book born to sell
counterfeits... No, it's the conclusion of many romantics...
No, victims.
Mage Relm: Hmph! This time, I can feel the satisfaction!

Stolge of Affection: If it's just a mere counterfeit, it
would be a joke... but there are rumors of dangerous
counterfeits as well.

Stolge of Affection: Well, if it's the genius of the
academy, there shouldn't be any problem.

Stolge of Affection: I'm going! Let's meet again at the
Adventurer's Guild!
Stolge of Affection: Are you ready?

Stolge of Affection: I'm in a hurry too, so please hurry up,
okay?
Stolge of Affection: It's very close by, let me guide you.
